commit.title: Micromega: fixed regression due to aggressive substitution
commit.message:
Micromega: fixed regression due to aggressive substitution

Eliminating a variable x using an equation of the form x = e
leads to an equi-provable goal. However, this may make the
proof harder (out-of-reach of current limited non-linear reasoning)
and is therefore disabled.
(The substitution would be safe if x is only used linearly.)
